How to prepare a new release:

1. Check in all changes.
2. Also change Makefile.version and check this in.
3. Update the ChangeLog. Use 'svn log -r HEAD:lastHead' in order to create
	the list of changes.
4. Tag the new release using:

svn copy http://svn.ipd.uka.de/repos/ParaStation/trunk/mgmt \
	http://svn.ipd.uka.de/repos/ParaStation/tags/psmgmt-version \
	-m "Tagging the x.x.x release of psmgmt"

